  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>현수막, 실사출력, 폼보드</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-21f67344-fef8-44e9-b0c5-dfe1f7a444d8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2ba7fad0-a2cf-4046-ab46-ac32a1ba1dc9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:506px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223942696807/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">데이터 검수</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">인쇄를 진행하다 보면 대부분의 고객님께서는 여유를 두고 발주하지 않으십니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0d1e1a96-4801-4f01-880e-d6b6894d3c5e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24126a4f-bb87-43b1-8ed7-039c2278f8d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a6e926b-ba0f-402c-b08a-f7c07aa68585\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0912dbb2-d845-4512-b0ab-0a2749fd8f5b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">실제 30여 년간 인쇄 업무를 해도 90% 이상은 다 급한 고객님뿐이었습니다. 그마저도 여유를 준다고 한 시간도 고객님 기준으로 인쇄업체 입장에서는 납기가 난감할 때가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-edddac08-9533-48d5-bcda-bcf49140e9a9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1e36150-96a4-49b1-81c0-685e648b2a3e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-358ac1a2-50da-40d8-8fe6-c20ad05b9b18\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a84f74f2-259e-42fd-8ab3-55cb4c84c4c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 실제로 더 난감한 것은 데이터 사고가 발생하는 경우입니다. 행사를 앞두고 인쇄물이 사고가 나서 행사에 막대한 지장을 초래한다면 이처럼 난감한 상황은 없을 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f5201a67-6f9e-47ae-afd0-01db18e21533\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-07492ac6-ec86-4322-80ae-923c1e2b614d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9be1752b-7bec-4c61-8045-52364ad2072b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8da3b481-391e-40b8-a87d-2debbf1d2e31\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특히 배너나 현수막 같은 경우는 사이즈가 일반 인쇄물보다 크기 때문에 용량이나 해상도 질문을 많이 받습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a7f595d4-d141-4a68-885b-c897eacf3e5f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d342ac49-8549-429a-a423-6afa80e970d6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c603f503-090c-42ac-9ae8-f5bec1647e84\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-171dc146-1242-478c-8112-448fec4ab8e5\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>기본 해상도</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1c3e8366-3e7f-4db2-b10e-9258b328c7aa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-755b61f5-24c2-4e2e-b8f3-dbd317d39682\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이미지나 인쇄물의 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5ee87ee9-96f2-48af-af8c-2419db9b58d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기본 해상도는 300dpi</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-78726843-5178-440c-8977-faebb5d35fde\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. dpi란 Dot Per Inch의 약자로 1인치 안에 점의 개수를 의미합니다. 300개 정도가 돼야 육안으로 확인했을 때 깔끔하게 인식하는 수치입니다. 이보다 낮게 되면 인쇄물이 흐릿하거나 좋은 결과물로 보이지 않게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca604296-a95e-4a74-8de1-348a8221c0cf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6a07928c-045e-4455-b041-c3f67da20387\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa7dae54-cf57-4c7c-89dd-b4d830ca2c0c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7e5ca8d2-09e2-4f96-b339-a6e630dbc5e3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 해상도를 반드시 유지하여 접수해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b546f3d8-40a7-4fd8-8bb3-0db0ab66ea31\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ce7b69ad-88a0-4842-a963-8166af858f6c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e2cc1005-65b9-42e0-b7e4-43adc9294016\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c74f3ce3-94b4-40fe-8339-2c5932cffa2c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 5,000이 넘는 현수막의 경우 이런 해상도를 유지했다가는 용량이나 데이터 전송에 차질을 빚을 수 있습니다. 이런 이유로 해상도를 10% 이내로 떨어뜨려 작업하거나 전체 사이즈를 줄여 데이터를 전송하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac8bb69f-0e4d-4fd5-bfcb-41375e552af3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c417af65-d2dd-4245-bea1-6ce2a24c1109\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6c2c3a99-11ef-4d4e-a6e8-81eaf8c9c192\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-52f7020c-10e1-438e-8ae6-97e080f7c764\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 부분은 반드시 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하여 접수하시기 바랍니다. 데이터를 점검해 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f89314bd-4164-4115-afb1-0d521ee87f64\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:471px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223942696807/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b24176b-9e97-4769-8c76-7b039f350c96\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223942696807/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aa2b6e74-3b98-4e7e-ab18-d4ef8d84f795\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223942696807/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a22095c7-dc3c-4daa-86ec-d7d0fbb7efb5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4e3b41ba-a19a-4a2d-a898-e2e8909b4be6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-619d43b0-3162-4770-92c5-6f31d12db5c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a48bcc8c-80cf-4fad-a1ef-48786e2d607c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2a11706a-36c5-4e2b-8a4e-68c8c96fa206\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>기본 납기</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-76f59243-dc57-43d7-9425-8c5c3326a6f9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-451b1dc5-5b8b-401b-97e7-0a9510ba9fdf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">게릴라 현수막이나 빠른 출고를 위한 여러 가지 대응으로 거의 모든 업체가 빠른 출고를 모토로 움직이고 있습니다. 통상의 경우 기본적인 출력물들은 1 ~ 2일 사이 출고되어 배송이 이루어집니다. 하지만 부피가 크거나 내용이 복잡한 출력물의 경우는 반드시 상의하고 주문하셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-12c07efe-a82b-4761-9278-95a8ecb50102\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-08bc281b-ad69-4d17-aeb5-16e11e8a897e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a8a9e3e0-28ed-43e6-8bcc-408b17456f81\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-073ccc90-fc96-4a14-86b6-6a2af3fddad0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객님께서 생각하시는 납기를 못 맞춰 드릴 수 있는 확률이 높습니다. 어디 업체를 거래하시든 납기는 반드시 사전에 상의하시면 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-481d8e43-4856-4748-b78d-0f59300d34dd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9cba0d5a-cb9e-40ce-87eb-33424ac0f480\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b09925f-95fc-4532-b1bd-b1484999fa0f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-905cd32d-122a-4156-9758-8fcf46dda4bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 이 부분도 대부분이 생산 일정에 따라 변동될 수 있기 때문에 1~2일 정도는 여유를 두고 발주하시는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fcd7f628-6eab-4606-a8b9-42334ed754c4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e8bbc715-74af-419f-839b-bc4aef109d40\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-42d27ac1-b19f-437d-9ab3-e6c2567c298e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9a125255-2cb6-42aa-b9eb-b445ddac3a39\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 100% 납기를 보장해 드리지는 못하지만 고객의 입장에서 최선을 다해 소통하고 있습니다. 반드시 문의하시고 주문하시기를 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223942696807#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79eba2a2-27d6-46f0-a2d7-3e8b209e30d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-31c83cab-ab04-4137-b68b-cc42c03862b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24ae41f1-f8fb-4147-9278-5edd398743cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}